Package: SimpLin
Type: Package
Title: Simple Linear Regression
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-09-03
Author: Kai Jeffreys
Maintainer: Kai Jeffreys <kai.jeffreys@colostate.edu>
Description: Runs a simple linear regression. Inputs two vectors, a predictor and a response, and outputs a list containing relevant information about the regression and regression coefficients. Depends on Rcpp and therefore will be computationally quicker than other regression functions
License: AGPL (>= 3)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.1.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Encoding: UTF-8
